{"tid":946971,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[走鬼]格老：聯儲局不應向政治壓力妥協","createTime":"2018-12-19T02:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T03:30:14.000Z","uid":57424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb7c5b25aa7981ee2d45aa7fc1ed25b0f9d600e6","tid":946971,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國聯儲局前主席格林斯潘表示，聯儲局不應該向政治壓力妥協。<br />\n<br />\n格林斯潘接受美國一個電視台訪問時說，他出任聯儲局主席近十九年期間，於作出貨幣政策決定時，比喻自己戴上耳罩，不受政治壓力干預。他說聯儲局聽取市場意見時有時會尊重，有時則不會，但不會因為市場意見而改變貨幣政策。<br />\n<br />\n另外，格林斯潘表示美股牛市已經結束，雖然未來股市仍然有可能上升，但股市走勢轉穩並大幅反彈的可能性已經很微，呼籲投資者應作最壞打算。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=331251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331251&d=MgGw1fxvt6eEJPHkMJ7ZSnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9d451741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331251&h=d7e75792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=331251</a><br />\n落個長命PUT, 下年買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcba035a65cef9cf74f71a311f4f8208bb627cea","tid":946971,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T02:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa0595a46b255e4236f03909f808adcccafc5ec","tid":946971,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:11:36.000Z","msg":"格老出名燈"},{"pid":"b5a16e71fc24aa3f0777de394a7468d76cf3afdc","tid":946971,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffa0595a46b255e4236f03909f808adcccafc5ec","tid":946971,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:11:36.000Z","msg":"格老出名燈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}